title="viewlet"
help_text="A directive to register a new viewlet. Viewlets are content providers that can only be displayed inside a viewlet manager. Thus they are additionally discriminated by the manager. Viewlets can rely on the specified viewlet manager interface to provide their content. The viewlet directive also supports an undefined set of keyword arguments that are set as attributes on the viewlet after creation. Those attributes can then be used to implement sorting and filtering, for example."
help_url="http://apidoc.zope.org/++apidoc++/ZCML/http_co__sl__sl_namespaces.zope.org_sl_browser/viewlet/index.html"
